Package org.neo4j.test

Class OtherThreadExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.test.OtherThreadExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, ThreadFactory
    public class OtherThreadExecutor
extends Object
implements ThreadFactory, Closeable
    Executes commands in another thread. Very useful for writing tests which handles two simultaneous transactions and interleave them, f.ex for testing locking and data visibility.
